snippet.title: Amber heard and elon musk's romantic getaway - all 4 women
snippet.description:
Amber heard and elon musk's romantic getaway - all 4 women 
Amber Heard and Elon Musk are enjoying a festive getaway to Chile together. The 31yearold actress and the Tesla CEO began dating in 2016 before parting ways in August this year, and although they recently denied a reconciliation, the pair have been spotted vacationing together in South America. According to The Blast, that were also spotted dining out on Easter Island with friends and family. The getaway comes after Elon, 46, admitted he was left “hurt” after his split from the ‘Magic Mike XXL’ ...
